Hardware
* Raspberri PI 3 B+ or newer
* DHT22 humidity sensor
* Binary Photo sensor
* Bianry Rain sensor 
* three LEDs(red, blue, green)
* bread board

Software
* Standard Linux distribution
* Node-red
* Node-red module nodes node-red-contrib-gpio, node-red-contrib-dht-sensor, node-red-dashboard, node-red-node-pi-gpio, node-red-contrib-string
* Any modern Android device(Iphone version not currently compiled)
